"Make sure these are handled by VIM and not the editor
sethandler <A-v> a:vim
sethandler <A-b> a:vim
sethandler <A-n> a:vim
sethandler <C-k> a:vim

nmap <A-z> <Action>(Back)
nmap <A-x> <Action>(Forward)
